'''Azimez n unebdu''' neɣ '''Azimez amsulan''' d asnifel n [[tama timirant|uzimez amaddud]] deg kra  n tmurt neɣ n ugezdu snat n tikkal deg [[aseggas|useggas]] i kra n [[ayyur (akud)|wayyuren]] anda yettusnifel useẓreg n [[tasragt|tesragt]] tamaddudt deg tazwara n [[tafsut|tefsut]] anda iraqqasen n tesragt ttusmezgaren (ttuwexren) s 60 n [[tasdidt|tesdidin]] ma d tuɣalin n uzimez aẓaṛan ([[azimez n tegrest]]) yettili-d deg [[amwan|umwan]]


Iswi deg tmerniwt n tesragt ar uzimez amaddud d asizek n wakuden n umahil d twuriyin n iden i wakken ad tlu (ad tesɛu) akud yugaren deg wussan n unebdu iy rennun ttiɣzifen seg tefsut, sin akin tt-drusen (tt-nqasen) ar tlemmast n tegrest

